[thinking] 
[thinking] I need a resource provider for the test, and I'll be using StringReader to read migration content. I’ll import necessary items and assert using a JDBC query. It seems like I need to execute two migrations (create and copy) possibly with inline resources. The ResourceProvider appears to ignore prefixes and suffixes. 
[thinking] 
